    "summary": "Paper reports discovery of WINERED-HVS1, a metal-rich hyper-velocity star candidate ejected from the Galactic center. Internal tables include spectroscopic abundances (MB99 and VALD3 line lists), four HVS search methods comparison, notation glossary, and catalog tables of chemical/kinematic properties for HVS candidates. External resource points to a Zenodo chemical abundance catalog used for cross-matching. Gaia acknowledgements are generic and removed."
